column16: Aubrey Huff grounds out softly, second baseman Dan Uggla to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.
Bengie Molina pops out to first baseman Gaby Sanchez in foul territory.
Nate Schierholtz hit by pitch.    Bengie Molina scores.    Aubrey Huff to 3rd.    Juan Uribe to 2nd.
Justin Maxwell walks.   Adam Dunn to 2nd.
